  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK701">
<l>kūṟāmai nōkkik kuṟippaṟivā ṉeññāṉṟu </l>
<l>māṟānīr vaiyak kaṇi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The minister who by looking (at the king) understands his mind without being told (of it), will be a perpetual ornament to the world which is surrounded by a never-drying sea.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
